_sText:
Very open bomb defusal map. 30 player spawn points with buyzones. Good for snipers. This was Jernau's first map and it shows, but people like it, so what can i do? :D

The soundscape will chill you to the bone!

Missing nodraw textures cause black streaks on the displacements. I'm not going to worry about this if you don't :) 

Jernau's Maps are available at http://maps.playerofgames.net/
